Bundled the previously standalone "Kustom Shipping Assistant for WooCommerce" plugin into Kustom Checkout. The feature is enabled by default and can be turned off with the new "Kustom Shipping Assistant" option under the shipping settings. If the standalone plugin is still active, the bundled version stays dormant and an admin notice asks the merchant to deactivate the standalone plugin.
